# VitePress docs site build outputs
docs/.vitepress/dist/
docs/.vitepress/cache/

# Auto-generated docs pages, produced by `npm run docs:data` (which
# `docs:dev` and `docs:build` chain into). Snapshots is rendered from
# `build/spec-*.json` pin headers; changelog is a verbatim copy of the
# repo-root CHANGELOG.md so VitePress can route it.
docs/snapshots.md
docs/changelog.md

# Staging directory the deploy workflow copies the built docs into so
# wrangler can bundle them as Worker static assets. Gitignored;
# regenerated on every deploy.
worker/public/
